# L9 CI-core bootstrap runtime dependencies.
#
# Only third-party libraries actually imported by the bootstrap gate scripts
# (.github/scripts/**) are declared here. Everything else in the standard
# library needs no pin. Compile with:
#
#   pip-compile --generate-hashes --allow-unsafe \
#       --output-file requirements/bootstrap.lock requirements/bootstrap.in
#
# on Ubuntu / CPython 3.12 so the resulting hashes match the runner platform.
